reviewText: Very cute movies. Grandkids love them.
Really great movie, also spoofing the Bond series--Kitty (Pussy!) Galore!!!
The movies are awesome for kids. My 7 year old loves them.

I took the movies with us on vacation.  I was extremely disappointed when neither disk worked on our portable DVD player.  When we got home from our trip they ended up working fine on the bigger DVD player attached to the TV.
Good deal for two loved movies!
